Package: mmer
Title: The Multimodal Marginal Epistasis Test
Version: 0.0.1
URL: https://github.com/lcrawlab/mmer, https://lcrawlab.github.io/mmer/
BugReports: https://github.com/lcrawlab/mmer/issues
Authors@R: c(
